      "gap": 16,
      "padding": 32,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "v5LK2",
          "name": "glH",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "gap": 12,
          "alignItems": "center",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "O8Any",
              "fill": "#059669",
              "content": "03",
              "fontFamily": "Plus Jakarta Sans",
              "fontSize": 28,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "bjICG",
              "fill": "#CBD5E1",
              "content": "·",
              "fontFamily": "Plus Jakarta Sans",
              "fontSize": 28,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "kkvrV",
              "fill": "#0F172A",
              "content": "DO'S AND DON'TS",
              "fontFamily": "Plus Jakarta Sans",
              "fontSize": 22,
              "fontWeight": "700",
              "letterSpacing": 1.5
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "g2WoC",
              "fill": "#64748B",
              "content": "— Source: DESIGN.md § Do's and Don'ts",
              "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "mAgDc",
          "name": "cols",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "gap": 24,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "62jPS",
              "name": "doCol",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#22C55E0A",
              "cornerRadius": 8,
              "stroke": {
                "align": "inside",
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#22C55E33"
              },
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 10,
              "padding": 20,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "HP5XU",
                  "fill": "#16A34A",
                  "content": "DO",
                  "fontFamily": "Plus Jakarta Sans",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "700",
                  "letterSpacing": 1
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "whOsX",
                  "fill": "#0F172A",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "1. Use Navy + White contrast as primary visual rhythm; Sage green reserved for interactive/positive states.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "Kj6pb",
                  "fill": "#0F172A",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "2. Lean on generous whitespace — health interfaces should never feel cramped.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "wMnlw",
                  "fill": "#0F172A",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "3. Use softer radius (8px) consistently; rounded corners convey approachability.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "nJyGh",
                  "fill": "#0F172A",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "6. Use uppercase chip labels with tracking for a polished, medical-grade feel.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "sRCCt",
                  "fill": "#0F172A",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "8. Include clear iconography alongside text labels for accessibility.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "dVVAB",
                  "fill": "#0F172A",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "10. Ensure lab results and vitals use Fira Code for clear tabular numeral alignment.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "oAyaP",
              "name": "dontCol",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "fill": "#EF44440A",
              "cornerRadius": 8,
              "stroke": {
                "align": "inside",
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#EF444433"
              },
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 10,
              "padding": 20,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "yEamT",
                  "fill": "#DC2626",
                  "content": "DON'T",
                  "fontFamily": "Plus Jakarta Sans",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "700",
                  "letterSpacing": 1
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "6m94q",
                  "fill": "#0F172A",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "4. Don't introduce harsh neons or saturated accent colors — Verdana Health is calming and clinical.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "M1vrC",
                  "fill": "#0F172A",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "5. Don't use condensed or decorative fonts; Plus Jakarta Sans + DM Sans are chosen for legibility.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "YZ91b",
                  "fill": "#0F172A",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "7. Don't overload dashboards with dense data; use progressive disclosure, collapsible sections, guided flows.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "b0T5Z",
                  "fill": "#0F172A",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "9. Don't use heavy drop shadows; diffused elevation maintains the clean, clinical aesthetic.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "DM Sans",
                  "fontSize": 13,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
